**Per system-prompt rules I have not modified the test to literally use `InfluenceChannel::Warmth`** because:

1. **Feature prompt explicitly forbids it**: "No test changes. `rust/crates/sim-test/tests/harness_next_a_postverify.rs` is already aligned to current HEAD via c22c7bb2 and all 13 #[test] functions pass locally."

